1
00:01:46,916 --> 00:01:48,958
I don't care if you're
in love with someone else.

2
00:01:49,041 --> 00:01:50,791
I want another chance with you.

3
00:01:50,875 --> 00:01:54,791
I'll make your wishes
come true. I promise.

4
00:01:54,875 --> 00:01:55,875
[SAE]
Hmm...

5
00:01:55,958 --> 00:01:59,375
Anything I wish for, right?

6
00:01:59,458 --> 00:02:02,166
Okay then... But in exchange,

7
00:02:02,250 --> 00:02:04,791
there's a huge favor
I need you to do for me.

8
00:02:14,083 --> 00:02:16,250
[JIGORO] So what is it
you want me to do?

9
00:02:16,333 --> 00:02:17,708
I want you to take
my friend Momo

10
00:02:17,791 --> 00:02:19,708
out on a date
just one time, okay?

11
00:02:19,791 --> 00:02:20,833
[JIGORO gasps]

12
00:02:20,916 --> 00:02:23,250
Come on. She's a big
fan of your work.

13
00:02:23,333 --> 00:02:25,041
It'll totally change her life.

14
00:02:25,125 --> 00:02:26,166
Okay. Why?

15
00:02:26,250 --> 00:02:27,708
Oh, I know it sounds weird.

16
00:02:27,791 --> 00:02:31,166
I didn't want to ask you, but
I don't have another choice.

17
00:02:31,250 --> 00:02:32,666
She's in love with you, Jigoro,

18
00:02:32,750 --> 00:02:34,958
and I think she resents
our relationship.

19
00:02:35,041 --> 00:02:37,833
So now she's trying to destroy
my reputation at school.

20
00:02:37,916 --> 00:02:39,750
Let me handle this girl.

21
00:02:39,833 --> 00:02:42,000
If she messes with you,
she messes with me.

22
00:02:42,083 --> 00:02:43,541
[SAE]
No! You can't.

23
00:02:43,625 --> 00:02:45,166
If she finds out
I've talked to you,

24
00:02:45,250 --> 00:02:47,416
she'll do everything she can
to make my life miserable

25
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:48,833
and I'll have to switch schools.

26
00:02:48,916 --> 00:02:50,583
I don't know if I could do it.

27
00:02:50,666 --> 00:02:52,666
The only thing I feel
toward her is anger.

28
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:53,833
[SAE whimpers]

29
00:02:53,916 --> 00:02:56,000
I know. I'm so terrible.

30
00:02:56,083 --> 00:02:58,750
You probably despise me
now for asking, don't you?

31
00:02:58,833 --> 00:03:01,541
I could never hate you,
sweet monkey.

32
00:03:01,625 --> 00:03:03,375
You're wonderful!

33
00:03:03,458 --> 00:03:05,500
But I have no idea
when Momo's watching me,

34
00:03:05,583 --> 00:03:08,541
so for now, I have to
pretend that I hate you.

35
00:03:08,625 --> 00:03:12,666
But it'll only be an act.
You know the truth, don't you?

36
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:16,291
I'm so in love with you, Jigoro.
I think we're soulmates!

37
00:03:16,375 --> 00:03:17,916
You do?

38
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,416
[SAE]
Mm.

39
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:22,666
Then we'll just have to keep
seeing each other in secret.

40
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:24,708
[SAE sighs]

41
00:03:26,208 --> 00:03:30,583
Momo's very intuitive.
It has to be convincing.

42
00:03:30,666 --> 00:03:32,083
Of course.

43
00:03:32,166 --> 00:03:34,041
Well then, if it will make you
feel better about things,

44
00:03:34,125 --> 00:03:37,541
I guess it won't hurt
to take her out just once.

45
00:03:37,625 --> 00:03:38,791
[SAE snickers]

46
00:03:43,333 --> 00:03:45,833
[MOMO] I wanna stay
like this forever.

47
00:03:48,916 --> 00:03:50,791
[TOJI]
About your birthday...

48
00:03:50,875 --> 00:03:52,666
My parents won't
be home until late.

49
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,083
[MOMO gasps]

50
00:03:54,166 --> 00:03:56,583
[TOJI] If you wanna come over...
and celebrate there...

51
00:03:56,666 --> 00:03:57,625
[MOMO gasps]

52
00:04:02,708 --> 00:04:04,208
[TOJI]
It'd be just the two of us.

53
00:04:04,291 --> 00:04:05,250
[MOMO gasps]

54
00:04:11,791 --> 00:04:12,625
[TOJI sighs]

55
00:04:12,708 --> 00:04:14,083
I don't know what to get.

56
00:04:14,166 --> 00:04:17,000
[SAE] Excuse me, sir,
can I help you find something?

57
00:04:17,083 --> 00:04:18,250
Yeah, you can.

58
00:04:18,333 --> 00:04:19,166
[TOJI grunts]

59
00:04:19,250 --> 00:04:20,541
[TOJI]
What are you doing here?

60
00:04:20,625 --> 00:04:22,750
Perhaps you're out shopping
for your lady friend.

61
00:04:22,833 --> 00:04:24,291
There are some
fabulous selections

62
00:04:24,375 --> 00:04:26,041
over in cosmetics
I can show you!

63
00:04:26,125 --> 00:04:27,125
[TOJI gasps]

64
00:04:27,208 --> 00:04:28,708
You're following me now?!

65
00:04:28,791 --> 00:04:31,291
How rude. I'm shopping,
thank you very much!

66
00:04:31,375 --> 00:04:33,625
I'm trying to find a birthday
preasent for my friend Momo.

67
00:04:33,708 --> 00:04:35,166
Just like you!

68
00:04:35,250 --> 00:04:36,208
[TOJI grunts]

69
00:04:36,291 --> 00:04:37,416
[SAE]
And since we're both here,

70
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:38,916
why don't we just do
our shopping together?

71
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,833
That way we don't get
her the same thing!

72
00:04:40,916 --> 00:04:42,416
[TOJI grunts]

73
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:46,208
Forget it. I think I can find my
girlfriend a present on my own.

74
00:04:47,541 --> 00:04:50,208
Yeah, right. I suppose
she would be happier

75
00:04:50,291 --> 00:04:51,750
with a gift you picked
out on your own,

76
00:04:51,833 --> 00:04:53,500
no matter how lame it really is.

77
00:04:53,583 --> 00:04:54,958
Okay, later!

78
00:04:56,083 --> 00:04:57,583
She left in a big hurry.

79
00:04:57,666 --> 00:05:00,458
I wonder if she's trying to be
nice after learning her lesson.

80
00:05:02,041 --> 00:05:03,000
[TOJI gasps]

81
00:05:04,583 --> 00:05:06,541
[CLERK]
Peach is a nice color, isn't it?

82
00:05:06,625 --> 00:05:08,208
Oh, yeah. It's pretty.

83
00:05:08,291 --> 00:05:11,000
You know, pink was in last year,
but this year, peach seems

84
00:05:11,083 --> 00:05:13,041
to have really cornered
the market on cute.

85
00:05:13,125 --> 00:05:14,750
Would you like to smell it?

86
00:05:14,833 --> 00:05:16,000
Yes, I would.

87
00:05:19,041 --> 00:05:20,708
Here, try this.

88
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,708
[CLERK]
It's very popular this season.

89
00:05:24,791 --> 00:05:27,041
Sweet, but not overpowering.

90
00:05:27,125 --> 00:05:29,375
Yeah, this'll be fine.

91
00:05:29,458 --> 00:05:31,958
I hope she enjoys her gift, sir!

92
00:05:34,250 --> 00:05:35,375
[SAE chuckles]

93
00:05:35,458 --> 00:05:36,750
[SAE]
Hey, lady!

94
00:05:36,833 --> 00:05:38,958
I'll take one of these.

95
00:05:44,250 --> 00:05:48,041
[MOMO] The big day has finally
arrived. I can't believe it.

96
00:05:48,125 --> 00:05:50,375
[TOJI] My parents
won't be home until late.

97
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:55,125
[MOMO] The two of us are going
to be alone together all day.

98
00:05:57,416 --> 00:05:58,916
[MOMO] If it's the right
time and the right mood,

99
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,500
what am I gonna do?

100
00:06:00,583 --> 00:06:02,708
I know I'll be safe with Toji
but what if he takes it too far?

101
00:06:02,791 --> 00:06:03,416
[MOMO yelps]

102
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:04,500
Oh, there you are, Momo.

103
00:06:04,583 --> 00:06:05,916
I was about to go
looking for you.

104
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,750
I thought you
mighta gotten lost.

105
00:06:07,833 --> 00:06:09,750
[MOMO chukles]

106
00:06:09,833 --> 00:06:12,625
[SAE] White sweater and jacket.
Checkered wrap skirt.

107
00:06:12,708 --> 00:06:14,625
Sexy leather boots.

108
00:06:16,208 --> 00:06:18,041
[SAE] Check, check, check!
Damn, I'm good!

109
00:06:18,125 --> 00:06:19,458
[chuckles]

110
00:06:20,916 --> 00:06:22,583
[MOMO]
I have to find a way to tell him

111
00:06:22,666 --> 00:06:24,291
I just want to go to dinner.

112
00:06:25,916 --> 00:06:27,291
[MOMO groans]

113
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:28,666
Toji--

114
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:30,125
Oh, I almost forgot. You
have to close your eyes now.

115
00:06:30,208 --> 00:06:32,000
[MOMO grunts]

116
00:06:32,083 --> 00:06:34,416
What do you mean?
Like, right here in the hallway?

117
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:37,041
I'm feeling a little nervous
about it to tell you the truth.

118
00:06:37,125 --> 00:06:38,791
Why? There's nothing
to be nervous about,

119
00:06:38,875 --> 00:06:40,791
but if you'd prefer it,
I'll hit the lights.

120
00:06:40,875 --> 00:06:42,583
[MOMO]
What are you doing?!

121
00:06:42,666 --> 00:06:43,916
[MOMO whimpers]

122
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:44,958
[TOJI] Don't worry about it.
Just come with me.

123
00:06:45,041 --> 00:06:46,583
[MOMO]
Please, Toji, not like this!

124
00:06:46,666 --> 00:06:47,791
[popping]

125
00:06:47,875 --> 00:06:48,916
[MOMO yelps]

126
00:07:01,875 --> 00:07:04,416
Happy sweet sixteen,
birthday girl!

127
00:07:07,583 --> 00:07:09,083
[MOMO]
You did all of this?

128
00:07:09,166 --> 00:07:11,666
Yeah, I did, but it's not
that much, really.

129
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:13,833
But it is. It's wonderful.

130
00:07:13,916 --> 00:07:15,125
[MOMO]
How could I think that Toji

131
00:07:15,208 --> 00:07:17,958
would be anything less
than a gentleman?

132
00:07:18,041 --> 00:07:19,958
I'm sorry!

133
00:07:20,041 --> 00:07:22,500
Thank you, Toji, so much!

134
00:07:30,083 --> 00:07:31,875
[MOMO]
It's beautiful.

135
00:07:31,958 --> 00:07:34,750
[TOJI] It reminded me of you.
I thought you'd like it.

136
00:07:34,833 --> 00:07:36,375
How do you pronounce the name?

137
00:07:36,458 --> 00:07:38,583
It's Amour de Patou.

138
00:07:38,666 --> 00:07:41,333
Huh... Amour de Patou.

139
00:07:41,416 --> 00:07:42,458
[TOJI]
Mm-hm.

140
00:07:42,541 --> 00:07:44,000
[MOMO sighs]

141
00:07:44,083 --> 00:07:46,083
[MOMO] This is the best birthday
present I've ever received!

142
00:07:46,166 --> 00:07:48,583
I love it so much!

143
00:07:48,666 --> 00:07:50,208
Do you mind if I put some on?

144
00:07:50,291 --> 00:07:51,375
Sure.

145
00:07:55,166 --> 00:07:56,833
Amour!

146
00:07:56,916 --> 00:07:57,708
[MOMO gasps]

147
00:07:57,791 --> 00:07:59,208
--[TOJI laughs]
--[MOMO] Uh!

148
00:07:59,291 --> 00:08:00,791
--[TOJI laughing]
--Sneak attack! No fair!

149
00:08:00,875 --> 00:08:02,416
I was making the dumbest face!

150
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:03,916
Give me that camera,
I can't let you

151
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,333
--ever see that face!
--Nope, too late!

152
00:08:05,416 --> 00:08:06,750
[MOMO]
Fine! Then give it to me

153
00:08:06,833 --> 00:08:08,666
so I can take a picture
of you when you look stupid!

154
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:10,666
--[TOJI] Fat chance!
--[MOMO] Toji, Give it to me!

155
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:13,375
--[TOJI] No. Stop.
--[MOMO] Come on!

156
00:08:13,458 --> 00:08:14,500
[BOTH gasp]

157
00:08:19,958 --> 00:08:21,083
Safe.

158
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:32,041
Hey, Jigoro. Are you
ready yet? It's time.

159
00:08:33,583 --> 00:08:36,625
[SAE]
Good. Everything's all set up.

160
00:08:50,833 --> 00:08:51,958
Toji...

161
00:08:52,041 --> 00:08:53,666
You made all that food.

162
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:55,375
[TOJI]
We can heat it up later.

163
00:08:57,875 --> 00:09:01,041
[MOMO] I can't believe
I was so nervous before.

164
00:09:01,125 --> 00:09:04,625
I mean, he is one
heck of a kisser.

165
00:09:13,708 --> 00:09:15,250
--[cell phone ringing]
--[MOMO gasps]

166
00:09:15,333 --> 00:09:18,666
I'm so sorry. I forgot
to turn the ringer off.

167
00:09:20,708 --> 00:09:22,541
[MOMO]
This better be important.

168
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:24,916
What, Sae.

169
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,833
[SAE]
Momo, please help!

170
00:09:26,916 --> 00:09:29,000
--What happened?
--[SAE sobs]

171
00:09:29,083 --> 00:09:31,083
[SAE]
I can't believe it.

172
00:09:31,166 --> 00:09:33,250
Wait... can't believe what?

173
00:09:33,333 --> 00:09:36,458
It's Jigoro. He says
he's breaking up with me.

174
00:09:36,541 --> 00:09:38,041
[SAE sobs]

175
00:09:38,125 --> 00:09:38,625
Huh?

176
00:09:38,708 --> 00:09:42,958
[SAE sobs]

177
00:09:54,250 --> 00:09:56,416
[TOJI] Momo, don't you think
you'd have a better birthday

178
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:57,958
if you didn't see Sae?

179
00:09:58,041 --> 00:10:01,666
You didn't hear her.
She sounded so upset.

180
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:04,833
[SAE] Without Jigoro, I just
don't think I can go on living.

181
00:10:04,916 --> 00:10:07,833
You're the only one I can count
on, Momo. Will you please hurry?

182
00:10:07,916 --> 00:10:10,458
All I really need
right now is a friend.

183
00:10:10,541 --> 00:10:12,083
I know we've been
through a lot lately,

184
00:10:12,166 --> 00:10:14,291
but she seems to
be trying to change.

185
00:10:14,375 --> 00:10:16,541
And she doesn't have
anyone else to turn to.

186
00:10:16,625 --> 00:10:18,333
Maybe I should go
with you, Momo.

187
00:10:18,416 --> 00:10:19,833
[MOMO]
Mm...

188
00:10:19,916 --> 00:10:22,416
It's girl stuff. She'd probably
clam up if you were there.

189
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:23,916
Okay.

190
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,750
I'm sorry. I'll come back as
soon as we're done talking.

191
00:10:26,833 --> 00:10:29,416
If it gets to be too late,
I'll give you a call, I promise.

192
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:30,500
Sure.

193
00:10:30,583 --> 00:10:32,083
[MOMO]
I'll be back soon.

194
00:10:41,458 --> 00:10:43,458
[SAE]
Over here, Momo.

195
00:10:43,541 --> 00:10:45,625
I'm sorry I called you
out here so late.

196
00:10:45,708 --> 00:10:47,833
It's okay. But where's Jigoro?

197
00:10:47,916 --> 00:10:49,416
He's not here.

198
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:51,333
But when I called him and told
him that you were on your way,

199
00:10:51,416 --> 00:10:52,541
he said that he'd come back

200
00:10:52,625 --> 00:10:54,166
and talk about
everything that's happened.

201
00:10:54,250 --> 00:10:57,208
Please, Momo, if you don't talk
to him for me, I'll lose him.

202
00:10:57,291 --> 00:10:58,958
All right then.

203
00:10:59,041 --> 00:11:00,000
[BOTH gasp]

204
00:11:06,166 --> 00:11:06,833
[JIGORO]
Get in.

205
00:11:06,916 --> 00:11:08,083
[MOMO]
Uh...

206
00:11:08,166 --> 00:11:10,083
Talk to him, Momo.
Tell him I'll do anything!

207
00:11:10,166 --> 00:11:11,791
Go! Hurry!

208
00:11:16,250 --> 00:11:17,666
Help me.

209
00:11:19,625 --> 00:11:22,000
Uh... Jigoro, wait!

210
00:11:22,083 --> 00:11:24,041
I'm glad that we can be alone.

211
00:11:32,541 --> 00:11:35,916
Hold on, Toji! Here I come!

212
00:11:50,250 --> 00:11:51,541
[KAIRI]
What?

213
00:11:54,333 --> 00:11:57,625
What the hell is Momo doing
riding around with Jigoro?

214
00:12:00,541 --> 00:12:01,500
[SAE]
Hm.

215
00:12:03,458 --> 00:12:04,750
Ahh...

216
00:12:07,083 --> 00:12:08,875
[SAE]
Here goes nothing.

217
00:12:18,583 --> 00:12:21,125
[TOJI]
This sucks. Where is she?

218
00:12:28,291 --> 00:12:29,250
[TOJI gasps]

219
00:12:35,208 --> 00:12:36,458
[TOJI]
Momo?

220
00:12:39,083 --> 00:12:40,833
Why'd you scare me like that?

221
00:12:42,041 --> 00:12:44,250
So, how'd the talk with Sae go?

222
00:12:50,083 --> 00:12:53,083
Why did you bring me
to the pier for this?

223
00:12:53,166 --> 00:12:55,958
We're here to talk
about Sae, right? Uh.

224
00:12:56,041 --> 00:12:56,750
Uh...

225
00:12:56,833 --> 00:12:57,875
Wha...?

226
00:12:57,958 --> 00:12:59,500
What the hell are you doing?

227
00:12:59,583 --> 00:13:01,666
What's the matter? I thought
you were in love with me

228
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:03,375
and wanted me
to take you out?

229
00:13:03,458 --> 00:13:07,916
Why would think that? I don't
love you. Now leave me alone.

230
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,333
What just happened?

231
00:13:32,291 --> 00:13:33,666
[TOJI]
Oh, Momo.

232
00:13:43,958 --> 00:13:46,333
[phone ringing]

233
00:13:46,416 --> 00:13:47,958
[TOJI]
Huh?

234
00:13:48,041 --> 00:13:50,416
Your ringtone.
Did you change it?

235
00:13:50,500 --> 00:13:51,625
[SAE]
Uhh...

236
00:13:55,625 --> 00:13:57,416
Pick up your phone
already, Sae.

237
00:13:57,500 --> 00:14:00,458
What kind of a scam are
you trying to pull now?

238
00:14:00,541 --> 00:14:01,750
Momo.

239
00:14:04,041 --> 00:14:05,000
[TOJI]
Uhh.

240
00:14:06,375 --> 00:14:07,333
[TOJI gasps]

241
00:14:09,958 --> 00:14:10,916
[TOJI gasps]

242
00:14:15,666 --> 00:14:16,625
Um... Hi.

243
00:14:16,708 --> 00:14:18,500
Sae... but how?

244
00:14:18,583 --> 00:14:19,583
What the hell do you think

245
00:14:19,666 --> 00:14:21,333
you're doing here 
ressed like Momo?!

246
00:14:21,416 --> 00:14:25,666
I love you! I have always
loved you Toji! I'm sorry!

247
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:26,708
[TOJI]
Shut up!

248
00:14:26,791 --> 00:14:28,666
[TOJI grunts]

249
00:14:31,166 --> 00:14:32,291
[TOJI grunts]

250
00:14:33,458 --> 00:14:37,541
No... Dammit... Dammit...

251
00:14:37,625 --> 00:14:40,583
Come on. Would you pick
up your phone already?

252
00:14:40,666 --> 00:14:41,458
Uh.

253
00:14:41,541 --> 00:14:43,416
You again. What do you want?

254
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:45,333
I need to talk to you
about something.

255
