to talk about. Go away.

257
00:14:50,916 --> 00:14:51,458
[JIGORO]
Hold up.

258
00:14:51,541 --> 00:14:52,416
[MOMO gasps]

259
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:53,875
Get your hands off me!

260
00:14:53,958 --> 00:14:55,125
[MOMO grunts]

261
00:14:55,208 --> 00:14:57,083
I said I need to talk
to you. It's important.

262
00:14:57,166 --> 00:14:58,750
I don't care.

263
00:14:58,833 --> 00:14:59,833
--[MOMO grunts]
--[JIGARO gasps]

264
00:14:59,916 --> 00:15:01,708
--[MOMO] Now, let me go!
--[JIGARO] Wait!

265
00:15:05,041 --> 00:15:07,458
[TOJI]
I'm not listening to your crap.

266
00:15:07,541 --> 00:15:08,791
You can explain that outfit

267
00:15:08,875 --> 00:15:11,208
and what you're doing
here some other time.

268
00:15:11,291 --> 00:15:12,833
Now where's Momo?

269
00:15:12,916 --> 00:15:14,666
She's with Jigoro.

270
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:16,333
I'm sorry. I didn't
wanna tell you

271
00:15:16,416 --> 00:15:18,125
but I think she likes him.

272
00:15:18,208 --> 00:15:21,458
I mean, he's a rich and famous
model. She can't help herself!

273
00:15:21,541 --> 00:15:24,250
You liar. Momo doesn't
care about that stuff.

274
00:15:24,333 --> 00:15:25,875
Call me a liar. I don't care.

275
00:15:25,958 --> 00:15:28,000
Why don't you give her a call
and find out for yourself.

276
00:15:28,083 --> 00:15:29,041
[TOJI grunts]

277
00:15:40,041 --> 00:15:42,083
[phone ringing]

278
00:15:42,166 --> 00:15:43,083
Who is this?

279
00:15:43,166 --> 00:15:45,208
[TOJI]
Where's Momo?

280
00:15:45,291 --> 00:15:47,458
[JIGORO]
She can't talk. She's busy.

281
00:15:47,541 --> 00:15:48,125
[TOJI gasps]

282
00:15:48,208 --> 00:15:49,333
[TOJI growls]

283
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:52,708
[SAE] See? I told you
she was with him.

284
00:15:52,791 --> 00:15:54,083
--Be quiet!
--[SAE gasps]

285
00:15:54,166 --> 00:15:55,333
I don't believe you.

286
00:15:55,416 --> 00:15:58,000
I won't believe anything
until I talk to Momo.

287
00:15:58,083 --> 00:16:00,958
Aww, Toji, you are such
a trusting boyfriend.

288
00:16:01,041 --> 00:16:02,375
[TOJI]
Put your coat on.

289
00:16:02,458 --> 00:16:03,833
Why? Where are we going?

290
00:16:03,916 --> 00:16:05,333
I'm gonna find Momo.

291
00:16:05,416 --> 00:16:06,875
And since you're the
only one that knows how

292
00:16:06,958 --> 00:16:09,958
to get in touch with this Jigoro
guy, you're going with me.

293
00:16:12,375 --> 00:16:15,083
[SAE] My legs are tired.
I can't keep this up!

294
00:16:15,166 --> 00:16:16,125
Uh!

295
00:16:16,208 --> 00:16:18,041
[phone ringing]

296
00:16:19,125 --> 00:16:21,458
Toji. Hey, I need to
tell you something.

297
00:16:21,541 --> 00:16:22,333
Kairi?

298
00:16:22,416 --> 00:16:23,750
Look.

299
00:16:23,833 --> 00:16:25,708
I think I just saw Momo riding
in a car with somebody.

300
00:16:25,791 --> 00:16:27,583
And she looked like
she was pretty upset.

301
00:16:27,666 --> 00:16:29,000
Wait, who was it?

302
00:16:29,083 --> 00:16:30,875
From what I could tell it was
that model guy Jigoro,

303
00:16:30,958 --> 00:16:33,041
the one who's been hanging
all over Sae lately.

304
00:16:33,125 --> 00:16:36,416
Anyway, it struck me as odd
since today's Momo's birthday.

305
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:38,000
Did you guys get into a fight?

306
00:16:38,083 --> 00:16:40,041
Okay, Kairi, listen,
I need your help.

307
00:16:40,125 --> 00:16:41,166
[KAIRI gasps]

308
00:16:47,375 --> 00:16:50,583
Oh, great. I don't know
which way I should go.

309
00:16:50,666 --> 00:16:51,500
--[footsteps]
--[MOMO gasps]

310
00:16:51,583 --> 00:16:55,541
[footsteps]

311
00:16:58,375 --> 00:16:59,458
[MOMO gasps]

312
00:16:59,541 --> 00:17:00,916
[MOMO]
No. Stay way from me.

313
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:03,708
If you come any closer,
I'll scream, I swear.

314
00:17:03,791 --> 00:17:07,291
[MOMO gasping]

315
00:17:07,375 --> 00:17:08,416
[JIGORO]
Stop.

316
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:09,875
[MOMO yelps]

317
00:17:09,958 --> 00:17:11,666
[MOMO panting]

318
00:17:11,750 --> 00:17:12,708
[MOMO yelps]

319
00:17:13,833 --> 00:17:15,791
[MOMO grunts]

320
00:17:15,875 --> 00:17:16,833
[MOMO yelps]

321
00:17:20,916 --> 00:17:22,541
Momo, I... Uh.

322
00:17:23,666 --> 00:17:25,250
[JIGORO]
Hey, are you all right?

323
00:17:28,083 --> 00:17:29,458
[JIGARO]
Momo!

324
00:17:31,625 --> 00:17:32,541
[KAIRI]
And you seriously thought

325
00:17:32,625 --> 00:17:34,291
you could get away with this?

326
00:17:34,375 --> 00:17:35,833
What are you
talking about, Kairi?

327
00:17:35,916 --> 00:17:38,208
I really don't know
what's going on here.

328
00:17:38,291 --> 00:17:39,916
This is something
Jigoro's doing on his own.

329
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:42,166
Then why are you dressed
exactly like Momo?

330
00:17:42,250 --> 00:17:43,916
I guess I should explain that.

331
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:46,708
I was thinking Toji might
be lonely after being dumped

332
00:17:46,791 --> 00:17:48,291
and that this would
cheer him up.

333
00:17:48,375 --> 00:17:51,333
I was just trying to make you
feel better, sweetie, I promise.

334
00:17:51,416 --> 00:17:53,083
You are so full of crap.

335
00:17:53,166 --> 00:17:55,875
Now take off that stupid wig
before I rip it off.

336
00:17:55,958 --> 00:17:57,791
Okay, fine... jerk.

337
00:17:57,875 --> 00:18:00,083
Anyway, Jigoro's car
seemed to be heading towards

338
00:18:00,166 --> 00:18:02,583
the waterfront so we should
probably look there first.

339
00:18:02,666 --> 00:18:05,166
I just hope Momo's okay
when we find her.

340
00:18:05,250 --> 00:18:06,208
[TOJI]
Yeah.

341
00:18:09,250 --> 00:18:11,625
[SAE]
Smart move. There's no one here.

342
00:18:11,708 --> 00:18:13,208
Well, crap.

343
00:18:13,291 --> 00:18:15,625
I could swear they were going in
this direction when I saw them.

344
00:18:15,708 --> 00:18:18,166
They're not here. Maybe they
to went back to his place,

345
00:18:18,250 --> 00:18:19,708
you know where he
lives, don't you, Sae?

346
00:18:19,791 --> 00:18:20,458
Yeah.

347
00:18:20,541 --> 00:18:22,208
[TOJI]
Then let's go.

348
00:18:22,291 --> 00:18:23,333
[SAE]
Hmph.

349
00:18:38,833 --> 00:18:39,833
[SAE]
I know this is the building,

350
00:18:39,916 --> 00:18:41,416
but I can't remember the number.

351
00:18:41,500 --> 00:18:42,666
[TOJI]
Dammit, Sae!

352
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:45,083
[SAE] Now hold on, maybe
I can say I'm his sister

353
00:18:45,166 --> 00:18:47,583
and ask the manager
which apartment is his.

354
00:18:47,666 --> 00:18:50,416
[KAIRI] Spoken like
a true pathological liar.

355
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:51,541
[SAE]
Hmph.

356
00:19:05,916 --> 00:19:07,625
[MOMO]
Where am I?

357
00:19:17,541 --> 00:19:20,208
Jigoro, why am I
undressed in this bed?

358
00:19:21,458 --> 00:19:23,000
What did you do to me?!

359
00:19:23,083 --> 00:19:24,875
Nothing. Calm down.

360
00:19:24,958 --> 00:19:30,208
[MOMO screams, cries]

361
00:19:30,291 --> 00:19:31,125
Come on.

362
00:19:31,208 --> 00:19:33,208
[MOMO crying]

363
00:19:33,291 --> 00:19:35,583
What perfect timing.

364
00:19:38,125 --> 00:19:39,666
Well, I just talked
to the manager

365
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:41,708
and he said that
Momo's in Jigoro's room.

366
00:19:41,791 --> 00:19:43,958
He saw them in the elevator
a little while ago.

367
00:19:44,041 --> 00:19:45,041
[growls]

368
00:19:45,125 --> 00:19:46,500
We're going in.

369
00:19:49,875 --> 00:19:51,125
[JIGORO grunts]

370
00:19:51,208 --> 00:19:51,666
[TOJI grunts]

371
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:53,083
Where's Momo?!

372
00:19:54,791 --> 00:19:56,000
[BOTH gasp]

373
00:19:59,041 --> 00:20:00,083
Toji...

374
00:20:00,166 --> 00:20:01,666
[SAE chuckles]

375
00:20:04,208 --> 00:20:05,958
[TOJI]
You're dead!

376
00:20:06,041 --> 00:20:07,833
[JIGORO]
Uh...

377
00:20:07,916 --> 00:20:09,125
[TOJI yells]

378
00:20:09,208 --> 00:20:10,166
[JIGORO grunts]

379
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,333
[JIGORO grunts]

380
00:20:14,416 --> 00:20:15,583
--[TOJI grunts]
--[JIGORO groans]

381
00:20:15,666 --> 00:20:16,916
What're you doing, Toji?!

382
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,750
You can't punch a model
in the face like that,

383
00:20:18,833 --> 00:20:19,750
it's just not right!

384
00:20:19,833 --> 00:20:20,833
I think he just did.

385
00:20:20,916 --> 00:20:21,375
[SAE]
Uh!

386
00:20:21,458 --> 00:20:23,375
[TOJI grunts]

387
00:20:23,458 --> 00:20:24,375
[MOMO gasps]

388
00:20:24,458 --> 00:20:28,291
--[TOJI pants]
--[JIGARO groans]

389
00:20:28,375 --> 00:20:32,250
Why, Sae? Why is
this happening?

390
00:20:32,333 --> 00:20:33,500
[SAE]
Uhh...

391
00:20:33,583 --> 00:20:36,125
You did it. Why don't
you tell me, Jigoro?!

392
00:20:36,208 --> 00:20:39,166
I can't believe you would do
this to my friend, you monster!

393
00:20:39,250 --> 00:20:40,916
[SAE grunts]

394
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,250
But, monkey...

395
00:20:42,333 --> 00:20:44,625
[MOMO cries]

396
00:20:44,708 --> 00:20:46,500
It's okay.

397
00:20:46,583 --> 00:20:49,458
How could you?
How could you do this?!

398
00:20:51,625 --> 00:20:57,250
[crying]

399
00:20:57,333 --> 00:20:58,500
What're you lookin' at?

400
00:20:58,583 --> 00:21:00,458
Did you plan this whole thing?

401
00:21:00,541 --> 00:21:02,375
You're insane.

402
00:21:02,458 --> 00:21:04,625
Is that true, Sae? Tell me.

403
00:21:04,708 --> 00:21:06,958
What? No... Of course it isn't.

404
00:21:07,041 --> 00:21:08,541
It was you.

405
00:21:08,625 --> 00:21:10,916
I can see in your eyes
that you're lying to me.

406
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:13,125
You're my friend, Momo.
I would never do that.

407
00:21:13,208 --> 00:21:14,666
[MOMO]
Shut up!

408
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:16,208
[SAE whimpers]

409
00:21:16,291 --> 00:21:19,375
Get out of here! I never want
to see you again. Now leave!

410
00:21:19,458 --> 00:21:21,250
But, Momo, I'm here
to rescue you,

411
00:21:21,333 --> 00:21:23,666
why are you getting so upset?

412
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:25,000
Maybe what you saw in my eyes

413
00:21:25,083 --> 00:21:26,875
was the fact that
Toji kissed me.

414
00:21:26,958 --> 00:21:27,666
[MOMO]
Uhh...

415
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:28,583
[TOJI gasps]

416
00:21:28,666 --> 00:21:31,416
Toji... kissed you?

417
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:32,916
That can't be true...

418
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,958
[TOJI grunts]

419
00:21:35,333 --> 00:21:37,416
Can it?

420
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:39,208
[SAE snickers]

421
00:21:44,583 --> 00:21:47,666
[KAIRI] Come on, guys, it'll be
okay if you just talk it out.

422
00:21:50,333 --> 00:21:51,833
[MOMO]
I'm sorry, Toji.

423
00:21:51,916 --> 00:21:56,291
I have no right to mad at you...
after what I did with Jigoro.

424
00:21:57,500 --> 00:21:59,000
[TOJI]
I'm sorry, Momo.

425
00:21:59,083 --> 00:22:00,458
If only I had gone with you,

426
00:22:00,541 --> 00:22:03,041
