would've ever happened.

427
00:22:03,125 --> 00:22:04,250
Why, Toji?

428
00:22:04,333 --> 00:22:06,333
Why does all of this
keep happening to us?

429
00:22:06,416 --> 00:22:07,541
Momo...

430
00:22:07,625 --> 00:22:10,166
