It's all over.

431
00:22:10,250 --> 00:22:11,833
No, it isn't! Don't say that!

432
00:22:11,916 --> 00:22:13,916
But... what about Jigoro?

433
00:22:15,125 --> 00:22:18,125
Hey, you didn't do
anything wrong, okay?

434
00:22:18,208 --> 00:22:20,291
None of this is your
fault. Believe me.

435
00:22:20,375 --> 00:22:21,916
I still love you, Momo.

436
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:24,333
You're the same girl, I promise.

437
00:22:24,416 --> 00:22:25,166
Toji...

438
00:22:25,250 --> 00:22:29,666
[MOMO crying]

439
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:34,000
You know what, Sae?

440
00:22:34,083 --> 00:22:36,083
You're gonna get it!

441
00:24:08,041 --> 00:24:10,958
[SAE] Momo is always putting
me down and I'm sick of it!

442
00:24:11,041 --> 00:24:13,291
What makes her think she's
so much better than me?!

443
00:24:13,375 --> 00:24:16,500
She thinks I can't have
Toji? I'll show her!

444
00:24:16,583 --> 00:24:17,916
Next time on Peach Girl:

445
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,500
"Peach Crisis."

